Base Rewards ProgramWeekly ETH Distributions: Rewards are distributed every Monday to active developers based on their onchain activity (e.g., deploying contracts, participating in hackathons) and Builder Score.

$TALENT Token Rewards: Users can earn $TALENT tokens through activities like:Referring Users: Inviting others to Talent Protocol, with rewards based on the referred user’s Builder Score.
Boosting Builder Score: Depositing $TALENT to increase the score (up to 4 points) or access premium features like custom Talent Names.
Interacting with Talent Mate: Engaging with Talent Protocol’s AI agent (talentmate.eth) on Base to analyze contributions.
Building Credentials: Developing custom credentials for Talent Protocol, earning a revenue share if adopted widely.

